during the year with a resultant decline in turnover. However, the first
quarter of the current year showed a small profit, reflecting an improvement
in transaction activity.
Turnover fell to Pounds 1.38m (Pounds 2.69m). Losses per share worked
through at 3.06p (3.03p).
