FT  19 AUG 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
DE BEERS, Anglos and Richemont led the declines in Johannesburg, as the
overall index fell 33 to 3,140 and industrials dropped 20 to 3,983. Golds
lost 22 to 942 on a weaker bullion price.
