Sony                      2,020        +2.1         50       +107.5
JVC                         580        -4.4        1.0           *
Pioneer                     433        +4.1       26.5        -19.9
Kenwood                     220        +6.4        6.5         +7.1
Aiwa                        160        +5.7        3.4        -22.7
