<TEXT>
KINNEVIK, the Swedish telecommunications and media group, intends to merge
with Korsnas, the fourth largest pulp and paper company in Sweden to create
a new diversified industrial enterprise.
Kinnevik owns 51.5 per cent of Korsnas's voting shares and 44.5 per cent of
